A 5 step plan for writing a short discussion essay includes: 
1) Planning or brainstorming on the topic; 
2) Writing an introduction that provides background information and a succinct thesis statement; 
3) Developing body paragraphs that present evidence and support the thesis; 
4) Writing a conclusion that restates the thesis and summarizes the key points; 
5) Editing and revising the essay to check for clarity, coherence, and organization.
